name: Consume Me
description:
Creator: NARS

Sara Shakeel—the multi-hyphenate artist, creative director, collaborator, and influencer—has not only cultivated a globally-recognizable aesthetic, but has garnered a cult following amongst celebrities, brands, and press. Her flair for all things crystal, glitter, and stardust has caught the attention of industry juggernauts and amassed a community of over a million followers on Instagram alone.
